{"tid":654400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如廁後，用梘液洗手真係好困難咩？","createTime":"2018-05-05T15:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T15:51:19.000Z","uid":142242,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7c7c0507249d9042cd03f8ce37b7f43d77428a","tid":654400,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"我係男，我都唔係潔癖，去完廁所都係用梘液捽10秒左右，保持雙手衛生。但我去咗學校、公園、商場等嘅男廁咁多年，我真係未見過超過10個男人大小二便之後用梘液洗手，最多求其沖下水就走人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我懷疑我以前中學男廁嘅梘液有九成都係我一個人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有如廁後用梘液洗手呢個習慣，我係異類？花十秒八秒，用梘液洗乾淨雙手，對男人嚟講真係咁困難咩？定係好多女人都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87937d2c76fc3373b30071a659f652b30b0db3e","tid":654400,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:15:47.000Z","msg":"點解一定要洗手?<br />\n條巨龍自己既點解會污糟?"},{"pid":"b94b5a44b07bd87a0ddf8213ebb6da6007902854","tid":654400,"uid":3063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"洗完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n摸一摸出口門柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de92b446918898e00c337585e1b3ce5c47594e24","tid":654400,"uid":126133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:18:26.000Z","msg":"覺得梘液仲污糟"},{"pid":"d94527ac5891cae01a8fee3a6743d9840b04892d","tid":654400,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過梘液唔一定殺菌，可能只係洗走啲油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdaec95fb445dd376182e9f2061d3a0106d86637","tid":654400,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"如廁後，洗手真係好困難咩? <br />\n利申: 出街日日都見到有人揸水後唔洗手，好撚多廚房佬唔撚柒尻洗手，屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce136a0cd7d2a31675decfc99bdb36b8322ecfb0","tid":654400,"uid":178303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:48:24.000Z","msg":"喺街嘅廁所一定會用梘液，<br />\n同埋喺屋企開大都會，但小就唔會囉。"},{"pid":"daaf5cbb8bb90f2e66230b449d98290d07f6b34f","tid":654400,"uid":11089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"有時商場d梘液用完又臭又乾<br />\n其實好多女人都係求其沖下隻手就算"},{"pid":"4b6e2e37867679dbac5fc28a6a0eb683ff9ad345","tid":654400,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"你理得別人洗不洗手，自己洗好就得"}]}